* &quot;Street Without a Name&quot; (1934)
*&quot;Le Roman d&#x27;un tricheur&quot; &quot;(Confessions of a Cheat)&quot; (1936)
*&quot;Pépé le Moko&quot; (1937)
* &quot;The Innocent&quot; (1938)
*&quot;La Rue sans joie&quot; (1938)
*&quot;Berlingot et compagnie&quot; &quot;(Berlingot and Company)&quot; (1939) 
